					Full Description



		Allied Electronics Corporation Limited (Altron), through its principal subsidiaries, invests in the telecommunications, multi-media, information technology and power electronic industries. The Company's business is grouped into two areas: technology, multimedia and information technology (Altron TMT), and power electronics with a manufacturing element (Altron Power). Its technology division includes technology and information technology (IT) products and services that are designed and/or adapted and bundled into an array of solutions for clients and customers. It manufactures power electronic and electrical components, including cables, automotive batteries, power transformers and multimedia set-top boxes. The telecommunications unit provides communications services and the IT division provides specialized software solutions and secured transactional solutions. It has a direct presence in approximately 20 countries, on over four continents through its various businesses.
» Full Overview of AELJ.J







