Company Description                    




                        Allied Electronics Corporation Limited (Altron) through its principal subsidiaries, Allied Technologies Limited, Bytes Technology Group (Pty) Limited and Power Technologies (Pty) Limited, is invested in the telecommunications, multi-media, information technology and power electronics industries.                    


